Getting what I desired?

31
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:44,960
Chancellor,

32
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,160
please don't be annoyed.

33
00:02:47,119 --> 00:02:47,960
Lin Muxuan

34
00:02:48,199 --> 00:02:49,559
is already in our hands.

35
00:02:50,119 --> 00:02:52,160
As long as we investigate his actions
over the past three years,

36
00:02:52,399 --> 00:02:53,639
even if he remains silent,

37
00:02:54,119 --> 00:02:55,080
we will definitely

38
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:55,759
uncover

39
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,199
