45
00:03:11,399 --> 00:03:12,000
You see

46
00:03:12,279 --> 00:03:12,880
the Blossom Contest...

47
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:13,800
Regarding the Blossom Contest,

48
00:03:15,119 --> 00:03:16,600
