49
00:03:18,160 --> 00:03:20,360
I've already prepared a gift for you.

50
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,759
Thank you, Chancellor,
for lending me a hand.

51
00:03:22,919 --> 00:03:24,160
I will never forget your kindness.

52
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,759
This was crafted by skilled artisans

53
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:33,039
according to my prized steed.

54
00:03:35,759 --> 00:03:36,320
Then...

55
00:03:36,679 --> 00:03:37,160
It's...

56
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:38,000
It's indeed

57
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:40,759
a fine horse.

58
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:43,399
This horse can travel
a thousand miles a day.

59
00:03:44,039 --> 00:03:45,520
Among its kind,

60
00:03:46,199 --> 00:03:47,520
it stands out as the best.

61
00:03:47,839 --> 00:03:49,919
I had hoped that someday

62
00:03:50,399 --> 00:03:52,559
I could train it to be a lead horse.

63
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:53,960
But alas,

64
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:56,839
it lacks understanding of humanity.

65
00:03:58,160 --> 00:04:00,160
After all, it's just an animal.

66
00:04:08,039 --> 00:04:09,520
The Chancellor Residence
is heavily guarded.

67
00:04:10,119 --> 00:04:11,639
Shadow Pavilion was
full of elite fighters,

68
00:04:12,119 --> 00:04:14,039
but they all ended up being annihilated.

69
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,839
With just the two of us,

70
00:04:16,559 --> 00:04:17,959
attacking head-on is not an option.

71
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:19,640
If we cannot attack directly,

72
00:04:20,119 --> 00:04:21,320
we must resort to wise strategy.

73
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,920
However, Zuo Wenan
is a deeply suspicious man.

74
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,760
Those who serve him closely

75
00:04:27,079 --> 00:04:28,239
are all trusted confidants.

76
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:30,839
I think of one person.

77
00:04:31,239 --> 00:04:32,720
If we can gain his help,

78
00:04:33,359 --> 00:04:34,959
